Classement albums et morceaux de : Susan Levine Biographie complète Susan Levine has been many things — a graduate of Harvard, a waitress, an actress, a mother, and a music therapist — but she has always been a musician. After a childhood spent singing in Medford, MA, Levine learned guitar in college and spent time after graduation traveling the country, writing, and performing before settling in Boston in 1998.
